   Precious Cargo
   Laying out core containers for packing prior
   to an ice retro flight in East Antarctica.

   On the news of an incoming aircraft,all camp hands begin the process of
   pulling individual 1-meter core tubes out of the below-surface storage
   vault and packing them into their insulated transportation containers.

